original_title: Jack Jack - Az igazi rocksztár az első próbán meghal
overview: A rockumentary about four Hungarian musician: Mester Tamás, Papp Szabi, Ganxsta Zolee and Tóth Tibi. They moved in together for seven weeks to record an album, put together a concert while they were recorded by the crew who made a music documentary film of the whole work.
title: Jack Jack - The real rockstar dies on the first band practice
